Package individual Description

Package related to the individuals to be used and the operations they perform or suffer. Has an abstract implementation of both the individual class and the individual list class, so that the program may run with different types of individuals/lists. Also has the events' class for events (move, death, reproduction) related with the individuals, all extending an abstract event that relates to individuals, so that more Eventual related to individuals may be used.
Author:
Miguel Rodrigues, nr 76176, Afonso Soares, nr 81086
